Further evidence is emerging regarding the modification of PhenoAge via Omega 3 intake and other lifestyle factors. A recent cross-sectional study of over 20, 000 individuals from the NHANES cohort examined the impact of Omega-3 fatty acids on phenotypic age acceleration (PhenoAge). The study found a significant negative correlation between Omega-3 intake and PhenoAge acceleration (p
